<D>__{she'll be away on friday between eight o'clock and six in the evening to visit the grants in glasalt. if she's to make the journey there and back in the day she's to have no distractions the night before. she'll take a light supper alone in her private drawing room and retire early.}
<C>__{ponsonby}
<D>__{she'll need to sign dispatches before she retires.}
