<D>__{there are important papers from }
<C>__{brown}
<D>__{it can wait. anything else?}
<C>__{jenner}
<D>__{are you sure her majesty is up to such a long journey? she has only just recovered from a severe head cold.}
<C>__{brown}
<D>__{if i thought she wasn't up to it, i wouldn't let her go, would i?}
